---
import Paper from "../Paper.astro";
import SectionHead from "../SectionHead.astro";
import Step from "./Step.astro";
import Finale from "./Finale.astro";
---
<Paper>
  <span id="install"></span>
  <SectionHead label="05 · install">
    <Fragment slot="title">
      <span style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-style: normal; font-size: 38px;">00:30</span><br />
      <span style="color: var(--color-ink-faded)">from empty terminal to</span><br />
      your <span style="color: var(--color-accent); font-style: normal; font-weight: 500;">first alert.</span>
    </Fragment>
    <Fragment slot="lede">
      No account, no DSN, no dashboards. Three steps: a Telegram bot, a chat id, and one <code>uv add</code>. The rest is already wired.
    </Fragment>
  </SectionHead>

  <div class="timeline">
    <Step time=":00" num="01" title="Talk to @BotFather.">
      <Fragment slot="body">
        Send <code>/newbot</code>, pick a name, copy the token. Takes 10 seconds, always has.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="visual">
        <div class="tg-card">
          <div class="tg-mini-head">
            <div class="av">B</div>
            <b>BotFather</b>
            <span>17:02</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tg-msg tg-msg-sent"><code>/newbot</code></div>
          <div class="tg-msg">Alright, a new bot. How are we going to call it?</div>
          <div class="tg-msg tg-msg-sent">orders-api-alerts</div>
          <div class="tg-msg">
            Done! Use this token to access the HTTP API:<br />
            <code>7824……:AAH…Dg</code><br />
            <span class="small">Keep your token secure — paste it into <code>.env</code>.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Fragment>
    </Step>

    <Step time=":10" num="02" title="Get your chat id.">
      <Fragment slot="body">
        Message <code>@userinfobot</code> — it replies with your numeric id. For groups, add your new bot and use the group id instead.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="visual">
        <div class="tg-card">
          <div class="tg-mini-head">
            <div class="av info">ℹ</div>
            <b>userinfobot</b>
            <span>17:03</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tg-msg tg-msg-sent"><code>/start</code></div>
          <div class="tg-msg">
            <b>@your_handle</b><br />
            <span class="small">Id: <code>1387261905</code></span><br />
            <span class="small">Language: en</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Fragment>
    </Step>

    <Step time=":20" num="03" title="Install. Initialise.">
      <Fragment slot="body">
        Drop the token and chat id into <code>.env</code>, add one line to your Python — done. <code>init()</code> reads env vars and spawns the sidecar.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="visual">
        <pre class="terminal"><span class="prompt">$</span> uv add snitchbot
<span class="c"># .env</span>
SNITCHBOT_TOKEN=<span class="s">"7824…:AAH…Dg"</span>
SNITCHBOT_CHAT_ID=<span class="s">"1387261905"</span>

<span class="c"># app.py</span>
<span class="k">import</span> <span class="m">snitchbot</span>
<span class="m">snitchbot</span>.<span class="f">init</span>(<span class="s">"orders-api"</span>)</pre>
      </Fragment>
    </Step>
  </div>

  <Finale />
</Paper>

<style>
  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 28px;
  }
  .timeline::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 18px;
    right: 18px;
    top: 18px;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0, var(--color-accent) 4%, var(--color-accent) 96%, transparent 100%);
    opacity: 0.35;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .timeline { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .timeline::before { display: none; }
  }

  .tg-card {
    background: var(--color-tg-surface);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    color: var(--color-tg-text);
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Text", sans-serif;
    font-size: 11.5px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    box-shadow:
      0 2px 8px rgba(30, 26, 21, 0.1),
      0 10px 24px rgba(30, 26, 21, 0.05);
  }
  .tg-mini-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }
  .tg-mini-head .av {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #5ab5ff;
    color: var(--color-tg-surface);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .tg-mini-head .av.info {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-paper);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .tg-mini-head b { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: #fff; }
  .tg-mini-head span {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--color-tg-muted);
    margin-left: auto;
  }
  .tg-msg {
    background: var(--color-tg-bubble);
    padding: 6px 9px;
    border-radius: 8px 8px 8px 3px;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
    max-width: 96%;
  }
  .tg-msg-sent {
    background: var(--color-tg-sent);
    border-radius: 8px 8px 3px 8px;
    margin-left: auto;
    max-width: 80%;
  }
  .tg-msg b { color: #fff; font-weight: 600; }
  .tg-msg code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    background: #0f1a24;
    padding: 1px 4px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--color-tg-text);
  }
  .tg-msg .small { font-size: 10px; color: #8fa3b4; }

  .terminal {
    background: #1e1e1e;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11.5px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: #d4d4d4;
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin: 0;
    white-space: pre;
  }
  .terminal .prompt { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .terminal .k { color: #c586c0; }
  .terminal .s { color: #ce9178; }
  .terminal .c { color: #6a9955; font-style: italic; }
  .terminal .f { color: #dcdcaa; }
  .terminal .m { color: #9cdcfe; }
</style>
